title: Hour 3 - Jay Monahan (04-17-20)
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Jay Monahan (04-17-20)
description:
Momentum is building for an MLB season to start in July with no fans in attendance, and Dan gives his thoughts on such a scenario. PGA Commissioner Jay Monahan stops by to speak on the effort to bring golf back in the near future.
